commit_message:
Merge pull request #2 from stjude/update_dx_version

Bump Ubuntu version to 20.04
Update sicer no control module to Ubuntu 20.04

Updates to ChIP-seq

* Updated parameter wrapper to replace spaces in path with underscores
to prevent errors later in the pipeline.
* Tagged outputs in their relevant steps
Using pip to install MACS2 which can manage the dependencies
Updated macs2 to use newer requests to match dx-toolkit requirements.
Updated report app permission so it can clean up files properly
Updated apps to work on Ubuntu 14.04 since DNAnexus does not support 12.04 anymore

Merge pull request #1 from stjude/add-license-1

Create LICENSE
